## CÁC CASE STUDIES NGUY CƠ VỀ VI PHẠM ATTT <!-- text, from page 0 (l=0.036,t=0.017,r=0.496,b=0.078), with ID acd701e4-181e-4664-aff6-e5934cea0761 -->

Summary : This image displays the logo for Icetea Software, featuring a geometric red emblem above the company name in stylised text.

logo: Icetea Software

Logo Elements :
  • Geometric red emblem composed of interlocking lines forming a stylised "S" shape within a diamond outline.
  • Two small red diamond shapes flanking the central emblem horizontally.
  • Company name "Icetea Software" written below the emblem; "Icetea" in thin, grey sans-serif font, "Software" in bold, black sans-serif font.

Dimensions & Placement :
  • Emblem is centered above the company name.
  • Text is horizontally aligned, with "Icetea" and "Software" on the same line.

Analysis :
  • The logo uses a bold red geometric design to convey a modern and technical brand identity.
  • The contrast between the thin and bold fonts in the company name highlights "Software" as the primary focus.
  • The overall composition is clean and balanced, suitable for a technology company. <!-- figure, from page 0 (l=0.893,t=-0.000,r=0.970,b=0.094), with ID 44b91a0a-dc23-4c10-a224-3f01adc6a436 -->

Summary : This illustration depicts a scenario where a masked thief is stealing documents by reaching through a broken computer monitor, while a person is running away carrying files, suggesting a metaphor for cybercrime or data theft.

illustration:
Scene Overview :
  • Main subject is a large, old-style desktop computer with a broken monitor screen.
  • A masked figure (thief) is emerging from the broken screen, holding papers/documents.
  • Another person, wearing glasses and a hat, is running away from the computer carrying a box of files.
  • The setting is a simple, nondescript background with scattered debris near the computer.

Technical Details :
  • No scale bar, magnification, or scientific modality present.
  • No visible text or UI elements.
  • Black-and-white, cartoon-style drawing.

Spatial Relationships :
  • The computer is centrally placed.
  • The thief is partially inside the monitor, reaching outward.
  • The running person is positioned to the right, moving away from the computer and thief.
  • Debris is scattered on the ground between the computer and the running person.

Analysis :
  • The image visually represents the concept of cybercrime, specifically data theft, by showing a thief stealing documents through a computer screen.
  • The running person may symbolize an attempt to escape or protect data, highlighting the risks of digital information breaches. <!-- figure, from page 0 (l=0.098,t=0.242,r=0.283,b=0.485), with ID fb871399-d01c-4299-af25-bf1eacf6a3d7 -->

Summary : This image displays a collection of logos from various social media and web 2.0 platforms, arranged in a scattered layout, representing the diversity of online networking and sharing services.

logo:  
Platforms & Logos : 
  • digg (blue and white block text)
  • YouTube (red and white, play button icon)
  • upcoming (red and yellow script)
  • last.fm (red background, white text)
  • flickr (blue and pink text)
  • del.icio.us (black, blue, and white squares)
  • myspace.com (black and white, three-person icon)
  • Technorati (green and white, speech bubble icon)
  • StumbleUpon (green and blue, "SU" icon)
  • twitter (light blue, white text)
  • facebook (blue background, white text)
  • MyBlogLog (lime green, white text)
  • jaiku (green circle, white text)
  • Yahoo! buzz (purple, white text)
  • slideshare (blue and orange, two-person icon)
  • LinkedIn (blue and white, "in" icon)

Layout & Design : 
  • Logos are scattered at various angles, overlapping slightly.
  • Each logo retains its original brand colours and design elements.
  • No additional text, axes, or annotations are present.

Analysis : 
  • The image visually emphasizes the variety and branding of early social media and content-sharing platforms, highlighting their distinct visual identities and the interconnected nature of online communities. <!-- figure, from page 0 (l=0.380,t=0.131,r=0.623,b=0.437), with ID 6ad1dcfa-eb16-4dc0-97bb-ac7b37922d46 -->

Summary : This is a cartoon-style illustration of a person with brown, wavy hair, wearing a green collared shirt, emerging from a hole in the ground. The character is posed with one hand on their chin, appearing to be in a thoughtful or pondering state. Surrounding the character are three colored question marks (red, yellow, and blue), suggesting a theme of curiosity or confusion.

illustration:
Scene Overview :
  • Main subject is a cartoon person with brown, wavy hair and a green collared shirt.
  • The character is emerging from a circular hole in the ground.
  • The pose is thoughtful, with one hand on the chin and the other arm crossed.
  • Three question marks (red, yellow, blue) are floating around the character’s head, reinforcing a theme of questioning or uncertainty.
  • The background is plain white, keeping focus on the character.

Technical Details :
  • No scale bar, magnification, or scientific annotation present.
  • The illustration uses soft, pastel colors and clean lines typical of digital cartoons.
  • No visible text or UI elements.

Spatial Relationships :
  • The character is centrally placed, with the hole directly beneath.
  • Question marks are distributed around the head: red to the left, yellow to the right, blue below right.
  • The composition is balanced, with the character occupying the middle third of the image.

Analysis :
  • The illustration visually communicates a sense of curiosity, confusion, or contemplation, likely intended for educational or explanatory contexts.
  • The use of question marks and the thoughtful pose reinforce the theme of seeking answers or pondering a problem. <!-- figure, from page 0 (l=0.452,t=0.570,r=0.627,b=0.868), with ID 97eac394-a9d3-4b7c-b24f-a40013cbf2c5 -->

Summary : This is a composite illustration combining images of mobile phones evolving over time and a stylized golden skeleton at a computer, above a large blue rightward arrow containing the Vietnamese text "CÁC CASE STUDIES" (meaning "Case Studies").

photo and diagram:
Scene Overview :
  • The upper section shows a sequence of five mobile phones, arranged left to right, progressing from older to newer models.
  • To the right of the phones is a stylized golden skeleton sitting at a computer, suggesting analysis or research.
  • Below these images is a large blue rightward-pointing arrow.
  • Inside the arrow, in bold white text, is "CÁC CASE STUDIES".

Technical Details :
  • The mobile phones are depicted in a semi-realistic style with visible screens and keypads.
  • The skeleton and computer are rendered in a gold/yellow hue, stylized and cartoon-like.
  • The arrow is solid blue with white, all-caps serif text centered within it.

Spatial Relationships :
  • The sequence of phones and the skeleton are centered above the arrow.
  • The arrow dominates the lower half of the image, pointing right, suggesting forward movement or progression.
  • The text is centered within the arrow, visually linking the imagery above to the concept of case studies.

Analysis :
  • The image visually communicates the idea of technological evolution (via the phones), analysis or investigation (via the skeleton at the computer), and a forward-looking approach to case studies (via the arrow and text).
  • The use of Vietnamese text indicates the intended audience or context is Vietnamese-speaking.
  • The overall composition suggests a transition from historical context (old phones) to modern analysis (case studies). <!-- figure, from page 0 (l=0.625,t=0.299,r=0.945,b=0.907), with ID a4230e36-e25c-4e55-a115-9688aada7c1d -->
